::Feline::

"Ahh, I was hoping DevilDuer would be my back up." she gave him a 
slight pout.  She then moved her chair closer to Zardus. She ran her 
hand over his shoulder again and down his chest.  She mover her tail 
up so it was brushing slightly against the back of his neck.  
"So who is this bot I'm supposed to be working with? I hope he's half 
as handsome as you are." She blew him another kiss.  "So what do I 
get if I complete this mission of yours? I hope the reward will be," 
she paused and looked Zardus up and down,"well worth it."

> 
> Zardus' eyes follow Feline as she walks back to her seat, looking 
at her

his chest 
> and up to his shoulder excited him, and he couln't get his mind off 
it.

> Zardus glances at DevilDuer for a moment, motioning with his head 
for the 
> other to leave. DevilDuer stands up, smiling at Feline and walking 
out of the 
> room.
> 
> "I think you'll manage," Zardus says to Feline as the door closes 
behind 
> DevilDuer, grinning, "From the expertice with which you've managed 
to 
> brainwash Devil, you won't have too much trouble."
> 
> Zardus relaxes in his chair, looking at Feline. "As soon as 
Bloodystrike and 
> Skulletron get here, I'll explain the mission. You'll be 
accompanying 
> Skulletron."
